title: Can Draven cash in on a Clone?
body:
Came across this in one of my game I was low hp being chased by a Draven...
I sent my (Neeko)clone to distract him and he 1 shot it and made his "cash in" sound as my clone died?
Sooo Does he cash in? I asked the guy but I assumed he thought I was being rude cuz we won lane hard.
